    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "lgb",
      "x": 1363.3406502645132,
      "y": 2189.1835826355873,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 332,
      "text": "意图　≈ GUI　·　chat / 命令\n\nAgent 内核　= CPU　·　Claude\n\n程序　≈ 源代码　·　SKILL.md\n（改一句话就改了软件）\n\n能力　≈ SDK 调用　·　extract·score·ws_*\n\n上下文+记忆　= RAM　·　Active context·reviewed\n\n文件系统总线　= 磁盘 + 接口　·　存储即接口：核心对象本来就是文件，MCP 暴露成 ls/read/grep，一次打通全部 CRUD（无需 list_models 等几十个专用 API）\n\n纠正闭环　·　score·save_reviewed·autoresearch\n\n能力包　·　/plugin install · Upload plugin",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "version": 428,
      "versionNonce": 1755427658,
      "index": "bHTu",
      "isDeleted": false,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "seed": 1,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781083865786,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "意图　≈ GUI　·　chat / 命令\n\nAgent 内核　= CPU　·　Claude\n\n程序　≈ 源代码　·　SKILL.md\n（改一句话就改了软件）\n\n能力　≈ SDK 调用　·　extract·score·ws_*\n\n上下文+记忆　= RAM　·　Active context·reviewed\n\n文件系统总线　= 磁盘 + 接口　·　存储即接口：核心对象本来就是文件，MCP 暴露成 ls/read/grep，一次打通全部 CRUD（无需 list_models 等几十个专用 API）\n\n纠正闭环　·　score·save_reviewed·autoresearch\n\n能力包　·　/plugin install · Upload plugin",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.3833333333333333,
      "customData": {
        "name": "lgb"
      }
    },
